  <main class="min-h-screen w-full md:w-[70%] p-10">
    <article>
      <h2 class="text-3xl my-5 font-semibold">
        <center>Privacy policies</center>
      </h2>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which MobilePriceBD collects,
        uses, maintains and discloses information collected from users (each, a
        “User”) of the https://www.mobilepricebd.10mblogs.xyz website (“Site”).
