      <h3>How we protect your information</h3>
      <p>
        We use a username, secure password, website firewall and other advanced
        security measures to protect our website and any data you may provide to
        us.<br />
      </p>
      <h3>Sharing your personal information</h3>
      <p>
        MobilePriceBD do not sell, trade, rent or share any of your information
        for any purpose. Third-party programs like Google Analytics may analyze
        your non-personal information.<br />
      </p>
